{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "脆鋼", "storyInfo": "在海布里區撤離時，自救軍遭遇了工人們的背叛，凱瑟琳被挾持，克洛維希婭失蹤。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是倫蒂尼姆市民自救軍......決定撤出城外的全部人員。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_729_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "損失比我想像的還要大一些。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些人決定留下，薩卡茲雖然摧毀了我們的據點，但是他們不一定掌握了我們所有協助者的名單。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們並不知道情報洩露得有多嚴重，很多人覺得事情還沒有那麼糟。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，可以假裝重新擁抱自己的平靜生活。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們看不到我們已經退無可退了嗎？", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼說，洛洛，他們很多人並不是真正的戰士，他們只是願意在我們身上寄託一點希望而已。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站在這裡的我們......大多也不是。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知該忠於誰的士兵，丟了工作的記者，對薩卡茲的盤剝憤憤不平的鉗工......", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "受夠了的普通人。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#9$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆市民自救軍本來就是由這些人組成的。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開倫蒂尼姆，離開我們從小生活的地方，不再是傳遞幾行情報，製造幾把武器，鬥一鬥那些薩卡茲雇傭兵......", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而是在一場真正的、不知會延續多久，也不知會牽扯多少人的戰爭中尋找到自己的位置，這確實讓人恐懼。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我們自己的倫蒂尼姆，應該由我們自己守護......我們一開始都是這麼想的。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們以為我們一直在奮力與那種恐怖抗爭......", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，等它真的到來的時候，它比我們想的要難以承擔得多。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#7$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，我並不知道我們接下來的命運會怎樣，我們有了一些朋友，但敵人卻也真正露出了獠牙。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能我們這些人也很快就會被剿滅，成了群遊蕩在荒野上的孤魂野鬼，最終四處飛散......", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克洛維希婭，別再說這些喪氣話了。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我願意來這裡，只是因為我不想被任何人恩賜一場解放。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都是。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是個工人，不懂得什麼大道理。我只知道，自己親手敲出來的工件才最值得信任。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想從那些躲在宮殿或者城堡裡的人手中救下自己的城市，我一個人不夠，我遇到了你們。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#12$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我們還不夠，就去團結更多的人，如果最終我們還是失敗了......", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，那我會接受最後的結果。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，洛洛，這不是還遠沒到說結果的時候嗎！", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快點快點，加快腳步，這種臭烘烘的管道對傷患們的健康可說不上有益。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#8$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，郊外的空氣總比倫蒂尼姆城內要好些。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據羅德島的分析，前面應該就能進入薩卡茲補給線的一條分支......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們回來了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶，情況怎麼樣？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確認安全，沒有發現駐軍，也沒有巡邏的跡象，那裡像是一條檢修通道，有一些不知用途的儀器。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說來奇怪，我們並沒有發現那條真正的“補給線”在哪。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，這條檢修通道應付現在的撤離已經足夠了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快點，小子，讓你的朋友們動起來，一時的安全不代表永遠的安全。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，我知道了。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去確認一下那些搶出來的設備，可能有幾件能用的。還有幾台報廢的爬行者，運氣好的話還能開動。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶！", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不是不相信我們的事業，也不是在因為失敗而氣餒。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我們能回來的，對吧？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想讓我給你什麼答案？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直在鼓勵大家，可我自己畢竟也沒有真的離開過這裡。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況，是以這樣的形式離開。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特，我以前偶爾會想......我們的運氣其實不錯。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生在倫蒂尼姆這座城市，有些值得信賴的朋友，有份值得付出的工作。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到了假日，還能去巷子裡的酒館喝上一杯，玩幾把紙牌，贏回幾個小錢。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，維多利亞從沒有真正太平過。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們造出的那些傢伙被送到邊境，用來對付薩爾貢人或者萊塔尼亞人，在他們身上開出幾個洞——但這些和我們無關。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只要待在工廠裡，往鐵塊上擰螺絲就夠了。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也經歷了痛苦，也有無法癒合的傷痕......但我們不用擔心明天要殺誰，或者被誰殺死。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們仍可以生活，起碼假裝在生活。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲來了，日子難了些。工廠被交了出去，日子又難了些。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#2$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但以我的標準來看，大致上還是屬於運氣不錯的範疇之內。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您對運氣不錯的定義到底是什麼？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是還有功夫站在這裡談論過去。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，不過是好運氣到頭了，沒人能在彩票攤上永遠中獎。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但沒了好運氣又能怎樣？大部分人都沒有好運氣，他們照樣能給自己找些辦法。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續忙你的去吧，“自救軍的頭面人物”，車床可不會自己打包。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做好你該做的事，就像你那時候答應我的一樣。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，怎麼說的來著？“我會走進每一個夜晚——”", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#10$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，奶奶！我那時只是......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後悔說大話了？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我會的，我依然會這麼做。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種時候，你和哈維最像。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱瑟琳斜眼看了下費斯特，轉身消失在人群中。費斯特的身邊，打扮各異的人匆匆行過，他們都很疲倦，但他們也都還沒有放棄。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特知道，站在這裡的人，都是最值得信任的夥伴。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想著這一點聊勝於無的安慰，費斯特輕輕呼了口氣，活動了下因長時間繃緊而僵硬的手臂。"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吹散那些被稱為機遇、時運或者其他名詞的霧氣，生活這次又會呈現出什麼樣子？"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特決定放棄猜測，而是去親歷它。"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特——", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傷患們都已經進入預定位置了，接下來，只要進入那條檢修通道，離開倫蒂尼姆，我們就暫時安全了。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到那時，我們會重新組建自救軍第十一小隊的，對吧。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，洛洛，我向你保證。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 8.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特突然感覺到了一陣輕微的震動。"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_metaldoorclose", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......怎麼了？", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#5$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#5$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠處，這一段地下結構的出口和入口，正在同時緩緩關閉。"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tense_intro", "key": "$tense_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管道在關閉？薩卡茲發現我們了？！", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#4$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死！凱瑟琳和克洛維希婭都在入口那邊！", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我一直在監聽附近的薩卡茲通訊頻段，我們應該還沒有暴露。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#11$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，總不會是控制線路故障吧？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#6$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，這些管道的大門是在入口處手動控制的。在進入前我就檢查過了，傳動結構沒有問題。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#10$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特的視力很好，他一向對這一點很驕傲，這在總需要點燈勞作的工廠裡可並不常見。"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而此時，他卻寧願自己沒辦法看得那麼清楚。"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "入口的另一邊，在即將合攏的縫隙中，他看到了幾個熟悉的影子。"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些影子一閃而過，直到大門徹底關閉，最後一道光消失在了鐵幕之後。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到黑暗籠罩了所有人。"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特勉強重新站定，他感到口腔中有血味正在彌漫開來。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他嘗試嚥下這股血腥，可是不行，他做不到。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "計劃裡沒有這一步！", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通道的那邊是誰？他們想幹什麼？！", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_411_1#4$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "random": "true", "power": 3.0, "times": 40.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼了，費斯特？你......你的嘴唇是不是在流血......", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#4$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道通道那邊的是誰。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是......我的朋友，十一號軍工廠的工人們。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們說，他們去看看還有沒有能帶走的設備。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能關閉大門的，只有他們。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g7_subway", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......湯米。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱瑟琳，我......這不是我的主意！這是大家一起決定的！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像救我的那時候一樣？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是兩碼事，凱瑟琳！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "湯米，回去幹你的活，找個城防軍，把這裡的事情告訴他們。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好......好的！我知道他們在哪！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，你們綁人的技術不如薩卡茲。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想找你的麻煩，凱瑟琳，我們相處了多少年？我們太瞭解彼此的秉性了。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，我們也不想死在倫蒂尼姆的郊外，死在那些怪物的法術之下！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是個鑄造工人！會用熔煉爐，會用車床，會澆出幾個還算像樣的零件。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，他們讓我們出城，和他們一起面對一場大公爵和薩卡茲的戰爭？開什麼玩笑，我用過最像是武器的東西不過是一把扳手！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱瑟琳，我向你保證，一切都會沒事的，我的舅舅在城防軍當兵，我可以和他說說，幫工廠裡的大家求求情。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們幹的那些事怎麼辦？我們襲擊了薩卡茲。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可以說，都是那些自救軍幹的，我們只是被逼無奈。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，你覺得他們會信你嗎？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可能之後受到的待遇會更嚴苛些......可是只要大公爵們贏下了這場戰爭，我們就還能回到以前的日子！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可是親手造出了倫蒂尼姆！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......一切都還會好起來的。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以前可不是個會把希望寄託在貴族身上的人。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還能有什麼辦法，凱瑟琳！你告訴我，還能有什麼辦法！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是......不想離開我的家。我只是想再一次走在倫蒂尼姆的大街上，偶爾和幾個朋友踢一場球。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不想死在郊外的彈坑裡，被炸得七零八落。我見過那樣的景象。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲們......只會做得更殘忍。恐怕我的女兒甚至沒法完整地拼出我的屍體。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，凱瑟琳，我不想對你動粗。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於你，反抗軍的小領袖......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？人呢？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本克洛維希婭所在的地方，只剩下一截斷開的繩子。"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？明明剛才還在這裡！怎麼一轉眼......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人C"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們這麼多人沒看住一個小女孩？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一......一定是某種源石技藝！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人C"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了......讓她走吧，聽說她也只是個裁縫的女兒。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願她在倫蒂尼姆的黑夜中也能找到個藏身之處。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆工人B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_659_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g4_fogblockadestreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#7$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......很臭。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#7$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你猜猜這幾天死了多少人？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別去東邊的那條巷子，那裡昨天炸了幾個感染者，源石粉塵飛得到處都是。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死！薩卡茲們的目的就是把我們圈在這裡，然後讓我們自生自滅！", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你白天去了運輸工會，馬歇爾怎麼說？", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡現在燒得只剩個鐵架子了。我不知道馬歇爾在不在那些死人堆裡，我沒去找。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#2$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾伯特區的人不全是蠢貨和懦夫，對吧？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#12$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是......挨了一記直拳，還在頭昏眼花。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要緩過勁來，諾伯特區的人們會反擊的！", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許，很快大公爵們會進攻這裡，到那時......", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，你什麼時候成了大公爵們的崇拜者了？你的抽屜裡是不是藏著那位威靈頓公爵的簽名？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#12$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們得靠自己！", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們能離開這裡的，我會為你們衝鋒陷陣，我發誓！", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#11$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的上一個誓言是守夜的時候絕不睡著。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我那時只是......！", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#9$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，做夢的前提是今晚我們還能找到點能吃的東西。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧了戴菲恩，她一直都有囤積的好習慣，把拳館的倉庫塞得滿滿當當......", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {